Not to be that guy but this thread is for discussing the Vayne skins. Your Karma and Yasuo concepts are irrelevant to the thread. Not to mention that I have seen them and think that they are poorly desgined in addition to being very cliched and uncreative concepts. They're basically Syndra without the balls.

EDIT: Not to mention that Syndra was an Ionian who thought "FK balance" and became evil. You want Karma an Ionian, to do the same thing and dress in purple? You don't think that's too reminiscent of another champion? Hint: {{champion:134}} 

And just because the dude has a sword doesn't mean he has to be some evil samurai. Do people have no creativity anymore?
